[I] A free, and easy to use implementation of the Network Time Protocol

[T] OpenNTPD is a free, and easy to use implementation of the Network Time
[T] Protocol. It provides the ability to sync the local clock to remote NTP
[T] servers and can act as NTP server itself, redistributing the local clock.

[U] https://www.openntpd.org/

